1
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:00,280
We've had her under control.

2
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,200
But...

3
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:04,040
there's another woman with her.

4
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:06,250
Leave the woman in the room.

5
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:08,000
I only want Su Xia.

6
00:02:16,440 --> 00:02:18,300
Fan, I checked the surveillance.

7
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:20,450
Su Xia was taken away by Xiao Qi.

8
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:22,730
Where is she?

9
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:23,880
I don't know.

10
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:27,320
Fan, don't go looking for her.

11
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:28,200
So many guests are here.

12
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,930
How will things be if you leave?

13
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,640
Xiao Qi won't hurt Su Xia.

14
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:35,000
His target is you.

15
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,440
Listen, I'll go find Su Xia.

16
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,600
You wait here.

17
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:40,170
I will find my bride myself.

18
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,120
What about here if you go?

19
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,690
Figure it out yourself.

20
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:44,960
Wait, me?

21
00:02:56,720 --> 00:02:57,360
Su Xia.

22
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:58,920
Su Xia!

23
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:00,920
Don't come closer! It's dangerous!

24
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:04,410
You're here.

25
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,440
Give it to me.

26
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:15,560
Okay.

27
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:17,760
No problem.

28
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,460
I can give it to you.

29
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:24,000
Kneel

30
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:25,600
and beg me.

31
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:44,480
Wait.

32
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:57,800
Kneel!

33
00:04:03,640 --> 00:04:04,480
Lu Fan.

34
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:13,760
Please...

35
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:19,920
Please

36
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,440
let her go.

37
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:25,560
I beg you.

38
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,040
She betrayed me

39
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,480
and left me

40
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:32,580
all because of you.

41
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:36,050
Since you want to save her so badly,

42
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:39,180
I'll give you another choice.

43
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:54,640
Kill me.

44
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:58,000
If you stab me in the heart,

45
00:04:58,159 --> 00:04:59,560
my hand might slip,

46
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:01,290
and she'll be all yours.

47
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:02,480
Come on.

48
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:05,560
Do it.

49
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:07,090
Lu Fan, don't listen to him.

50
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:08,400
Do it.

51
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,360
Do it!

52
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,800
Do it, you coward!

53
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,840
Lu Fan. Lu Fan!

54
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:15,880
Come on.

55
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:21,240
Come on!

56
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:24,120
Come on.

57
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:36,200
Let go! Let go! Let go!

58
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:41,200
No! Let go! Let go!

59
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:45,720
It's okay.

60
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:48,260
If we die, we die together.

61
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,200
I love you.

62
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:59,040
I love you.

63
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:03,560
I love you.

64
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:35,159
Just leave.

65
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,400
Su Xia.

66
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:56,780
I didn't use you last time.

67
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,560
I'm serious.

68
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:10,080
I won't appear in your life anymore.

69
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,240
Let's go.

70
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,680
Su Xia.

71
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,000
Without me,

72
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,940
you must live in the light.

73
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,600
What are you going to say to her?

74
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,800
"Sorry, I lied to you.

75
00:08:57,800 --> 00:08:58,640
This is just a setup.

76
00:08:58,640 --> 00:08:59,960
I'm here to destroy you."

77
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:02,090
Or you just can't bear to part with her?

78
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:10,200
Have you forgotten how we survived

79
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,680
these years?

80
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:14,160
Have you forgotten how the Lu family

81
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:15,520
forced our two families to death

82
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,720
and ruined our lives?

83
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:37,880
What is your name?

84
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:39,560
My name is Su Xia.

85
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,200
My name is Xiao Qi.

86
00:11:10,680 --> 00:11:11,440
Xiao Qi.

87
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,360
You were once

88
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:17,880
the light in my life.

89
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:19,880
[Tomb of Xiao Qi, My Best Friend]

90
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:21,440
You held my hand

91
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:25,210
and pulled me out of the abyss
time and time again.

92
00:11:30,760 --> 00:11:32,760
But I couldn't hold onto you.

93
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,160
Let's go.

94
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:15,160
Everyone in Huishan knows

95
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:18,880
that today is the anniversary
of the Lu family madam's death.

96
00:12:18,880 --> 00:12:20,140
Every year on this day,

97
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:21,940
no one is allowed to get in!

98
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,760
Today is my father's death anniversary.

99
00:12:25,760 --> 00:12:27,040
Get out of here, all of you.

100
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:27,760
Stop it!

101
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:30,840
What a scandal!

102
00:12:37,400 --> 00:12:38,200
Young Master.

103
00:12:59,040 --> 00:12:59,680
Brother.

104
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:01,600
My Lady,

105
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,080
when did you get back?

106
00:13:03,560 --> 00:13:05,720
M-My Lady?

107
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:07,880
Mr. Lu, I had no idea.

108
00:13:09,280 --> 00:13:10,540
Don't call me Brother.

109
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,640
You don't deserve to.

110
00:13:15,800 --> 00:13:17,930
No one is allowed to disturb my mother.

111
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:24,760
I'll just leave a bouquet for my father.

112
00:13:24,760 --> 00:13:26,760
I absolutely won't disturb Auntie.

113
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:29,580
Please let me in, Brother.

114
00:13:30,040 --> 00:13:32,900
You should show some attitude
when asking for help.

115
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:41,940
Please let me in, Brother.

116
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:48,920
You want to play
the dutiful daughter, huh?

117
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:52,640
Fine, I will grant your wish.

118
00:13:58,440 --> 00:14:00,240
Kneel here until dawn tomorrow.

119
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:05,080
If you dare take a step
into the Lu family's territory,

120
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:08,000
I will make your life miserable.

121
00:14:11,400 --> 00:14:13,680
Before the cemetery
opens tomorrow morning,

122
00:14:13,680 --> 00:14:14,840
do not open the gates.

123
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:15,480
Yes.

124
00:14:16,560 --> 00:14:17,360
Young Master,

125
00:14:17,480 --> 00:14:19,400
she is a girl after all.

126
00:14:19,560 --> 00:14:22,160
Staying in the cemetery
for a night might be...

127
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,620
What are you afraid of?

128
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:17,720
Dad.

129
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:21,800
I'm back.

130
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:24,160
Dad, I beg you.

131
00:15:24,160 --> 00:15:25,440
Answer the phone!

132
00:15:25,800 --> 00:15:28,080
Sister, what's wrong with Dad?

133
00:15:29,640 --> 00:15:30,280
Dad!

134
00:15:30,680 --> 00:15:31,680
Dad!

135
00:15:31,800 --> 00:15:32,720
Don't jump!

136
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:33,600
Dad!

137
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:35,120
Dad!

138
00:15:50,480 --> 00:15:51,940
What the Lu family owes you

139
00:15:53,800 --> 00:15:54,840
should be paid back now.
